languages.text: "Я больше предпочитаю натюрморты или пейзажи. Но благодарю за заботу о моем художественном образовании".
"Personally, I prefer still life and landscapes. However, I appreciate your concern for my artistic education."
languages.original_text: "Я больше предпочитаю натюрморты или пейзажи. Но благодарю за заботу о моем художественном образовании".

traits.locale_text: "I am more partial to still life and landscapes. However, I appreciate you concerning yourself with my artistic education."
traits.speaker: CassiaCompanion

languages.text: 「個人的には、静物と風景が好きです。ですが、私の芸術教育を心配してくれてありがとうございます」
languages.original_text: "Personally, I prefer still life and landscapes. However, I appreciate your concern for my artistic education."

languages.text: "Ich persönlich bevorzuge Stillleben und Landschaften. Ich weiß Eure Sorge um meine künstlerische Ausbildung jedoch zu schätzen."
languages.original_text: "Personally, I prefer still life and landscapes. However, I appreciate your concern for my artistic education."
